            <!-- Q12 -->
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        已知矩阵  <m> \boldsymbol{A}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}0  &amp;  -1  &amp;  1 \\ 2  &amp;  -3  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0\end{array}\right) </m> . 求  <m> \boldsymbol{A}^{99} </m>

                    </p>
                </statement>
                <answer>
                    <p>
                        解: 利用相似对角化
                    <me> 
                    |\lambda \boldsymbol{E}-\boldsymbol{A}|=\left|\begin{array}{ccc}
                    \lambda  &amp;  1  &amp;  -1 \\
                    -2  &amp;  \lambda+3  &amp;  0 \\
                    0  &amp;  0  &amp;  \lambda
                    \end{array}\right|=\left|\begin{array}{cc}
                    \lambda  &amp;  1 \\
                    -2  &amp;  \lambda+3
                    \end{array}\right|\lambda 
                    =\lambda(\lambda+1)(\lambda+2) 
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 于是  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  的特征值为  <m> 0,-1,-2 </m>  . </p> 

                    <p> 下面算  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  的特征向量, 当  <m> \lambda_{1}=0 </m>  时, 解  <m> -\boldsymbol{A x}=\mathbf{0} </m>  方程, 即解  <m> \boldsymbol{A x}=\mathbf{0} </m>  </p> 

                    <p>  </p> 

                    <p>  <m> \boldsymbol{A}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}0  &amp;  -1  &amp;  1 \\ 2  &amp;  -3  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0\end{array}\right) \xrightarrow[-r_{2}]{r_1\leftrightarrow r_{2}}\left(\begin{array}{ccc}2  &amp;  -3  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  1  &amp;  -1 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0\end{array}\right)\xrightarrow[]{r_1+ 3r_{2}}\left(\begin{array}{ccc}2  &amp;  0  &amp;  -3 \\ 0  &amp;  1  &amp;  -1 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0\end{array}\right)  </m>  </p> 

                    <p> 同解方程  <m> \left\{\begin{array}{c}2 x_{1}=3 x_{3}, \\ x_{2}=x_{3},\end{array}\right. </m>  得特征向量为  <m> \alpha_{1}=\left(\begin{array}{l}3 \\ 2 \\ 2\end{array}\right) </m>  </p> 

                    <p> 当  <m> \lambda_{2}=-1 </m>  时, 解  <m> (-\boldsymbol{E}-\boldsymbol{A}) \boldsymbol{x}=\mathbf{0} </m>  方程, </p> 

                    <p>  <me> -\boldsymbol{E}-\boldsymbol{A}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}-1  &amp;  1  &amp;  -1 \\ -2  &amp;  2  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  -1\end{array}\right) \xrightarrow[-r_{1}]{r_1- r_{3}}\left(\begin{array}{ccc}1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  0 \\ -2  &amp;  2  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  -1\end{array}\right)\xrightarrow[]{r_1+ 3r_{2}}\left(\begin{array}{ccc}1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0\end{array}\right)  </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 同解方程  <m> \left\{\begin{array}{c} x_{1}= x_{2}, \\ x_{3}=0,\end{array}\right. </m>  得特征向量为  <m> \alpha_{2}=\left(\begin{array}{l}1 \\ 1 \\ 0\end{array}\right) </m>  </p> 

                    <p>  <m> \lambda \boldsymbol{E}-\boldsymbol{A}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}\lambda  &amp;  1  &amp;  -1 \\ -2  &amp;  \lambda+3  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  \lambda\end{array}\right) </m>  当  <m> \lambda_{3}=-2 </m>  时, 解  <m> (-2 \boldsymbol{E}-\boldsymbol{A}) \boldsymbol{x}=\mathbf{0} </m>  </p> 

                    <p>  <me>  -2 \boldsymbol{E}-\boldsymbol{A}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}-2  &amp;  1  &amp;  -1 \\ -2  &amp;  1  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  -2\end{array}\right) \xrightarrow[r_{1}+r_{3}]{ -\frac 12 r_{3}}\left(\begin{array}{ccc}-2  &amp;  1  &amp;  0 \\ -2  &amp;  1  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1\end{array}\right) \rightarrow\left(\begin{array}{ccc}2  &amp;  -1  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0\end{array}\right)  </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 同解方程  <m> \left\{\begin{array}{c}2 x_{1}=x_{2}, \\ x_{3}=0,\end{array}\right. </m>  得特征向量为  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}=\left(\begin{array}{l}1 \\ 2 \\ 0\end{array}\right) </m>  </p> 

                    <p> 因此  <m> \boldsymbol{P}=\left(\begin{array}{lll}3  &amp;  1  &amp;  1 \\ 2  &amp;  1  &amp;  2 \\ 2  &amp;  0  &amp;  0\end{array}\right) </m> , 则   <m> \boldsymbol{P}^{-1} \boldsymbol{A P}=\left(\begin{array}{lll}0  &amp;   &amp;  \\  &amp;  -1  &amp;  \\  &amp;   &amp;  -2\end{array}\right) </m>  , 
                    所以  <m> \boldsymbol{A}=\boldsymbol{P}\left(\begin{array}{lll}0  &amp;   &amp;  \\  &amp;  -1  &amp;  \\  &amp;   &amp;  -2\end{array}\right) \boldsymbol{P}^{-1} </m>  </p> 

                    <p>  <me>  \begin{array}{l}\boldsymbol{A}^{99}=\boldsymbol{P}\left(\begin{array}{ccc}0  &amp;   &amp;  \\  &amp;  -1  &amp;  \\  &amp;   &amp;  -2\end{array}\right)^{99} \boldsymbol{P}^{-1}\\=\left(\begin{array}{lll}3  &amp;  1  &amp;  1 \\ 2  &amp;  1  &amp;  2 \\ 2  &amp;  0  &amp;  0\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{lll}0 &amp;  &amp;  \\  &amp;  (-1)^{99} &amp;  \\ &amp;   &amp; (-2)^{99}\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{ccc}0  &amp;  0  &amp;  \frac{1}{2} \\ 2  &amp;  -1  &amp;  -2 \\ -1  &amp;  1  &amp;  \frac{1}{2}\end{array}\right) \\ =\left(\begin{array}{ccc}2^{99}-2  &amp;  1-2^{99}  &amp;  2-2^{98} \\ 2^{100}-2  &amp;  1-2^{100}  &amp;  2-2^{99} \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0\end{array}\right) \\\end{array}  </me>
                        
                    </p>
                </answer>
            </exercise>

            <!-- Q13 -->
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        设  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  为  <m> 3 </m>  阶实对称矩阵,  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  的秩为  <m> 2 </m>  , 且  <m> \boldsymbol{A}\left(\begin{array}{cc}1  &amp;  1 \\ 0  &amp;  0 \\ -1  &amp;  1\end{array}\right)=\left(\begin{array}{cc}-1  &amp;  1 \\ 0  &amp;  0 \\ 1  &amp;  1\end{array}\right) </m> . </p> 

                    <p> (I)求  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  的所有特征值和特征向量; 
                    (II)求矩阵  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m> . 
                    </p>
                </statement>
                <answer>
                    <p>
                        解：(I)  <m> \boldsymbol{A}\left(\begin{array}{c}1 \\ 0 \\ -1\end{array}\right)=-\left(\begin{array}{c}1 \\ 0 \\ -1\end{array}\right), \boldsymbol{A}\left(\begin{array}{l}1 \\ 0 \\ 1\end{array}\right)=\left(\begin{array}{l}1 \\ 0 \\ 1\end{array}\right) </m> .
                        所以  <m> 1,-1 </m>  为  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  的特征值,
                        因为  <m> r(\boldsymbol{A})=2 \Rightarrow|\boldsymbol{A}|=0 </m> , 所以  <m> 0 </m>  为  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  的特征值. </p> 

                        <p>  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}=(1,0,1)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>  与  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}=(1,0,-1)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>  分别为特征值  <m> 1 </m>  与  <m> -1 </m>  的特征向量,设  <m> \boldsymbol{\xi}=\left(x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}\right)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>  为  <m> 0 </m>  的特征向量.  <m> \boldsymbol{\xi} </m>  与  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2} </m>  都正交, 则有  <m> \left\{\begin{array}{l}x_{1}+x_{3}=0 \\ x_{1}-x_{3}=0\end{array} \Rightarrow\left\{\begin{array}{l}x_{1}=0 \\ x_{3}=0\end{array}\right.\right. </m>  所以  <m> \boldsymbol{\xi}=k_{3}(0,1,0)^{\mathrm{T}} </m> , <m> k_{3}  </m>  为任意非零常数.  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  的全部特征值为  <m> 1,-1,0 </m> , 其对应的所有特征向量为,  <m> k_{1}(1,0,1)^{\mathrm{T}}, k_{2}(1,0,-1)^{\mathrm{T}}, k_{3}(0,1,0)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>  .  <m> k_{1}, k_{2}, k_{3} </m>  为任意非零常数. </p> 

                        <p> (II) 法1: 可逆矩阵  <m> \boldsymbol{P}=\left(\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\xi}\right) </m> , 所以  <m> \boldsymbol{A}=\boldsymbol{P}\left(\begin{array}{ccc}1  &amp;  1  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1 \\ 1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  0\end{array}\right) </m> , 使得  <m> \boldsymbol{P}^{-1} \boldsymbol{A} \boldsymbol{P}=\boldsymbol{\Lambda}=\left(\begin{array}{lll}1  &amp;   &amp;  \\  &amp;  -1  &amp;  \\  &amp;   &amp;  0\end{array}\right) </m> , 所以 </p> 

                        <p>  <me> \begin{array}{l} \boldsymbol{A}=\boldsymbol{P}\left(\begin{array}{ccc}1  &amp;   &amp;  \\  &amp;  -1  &amp;  \\  &amp;   &amp;  0\end{array}\right) \boldsymbol{P}^{-1} \\ =\left(\begin{array}{ccc}1  &amp;  1  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1 \\ 1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  0\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{ccc}1  &amp;   &amp;  \\  &amp;  -1  &amp;  \\  &amp;   &amp;  0\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{ccc}1  &amp;  1  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1 \\ 1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  0\end{array}\right)^{-1}\\=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}1  &amp;  1  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1 \\ 1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  0\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{ccc}1  &amp;  &amp;  \\  &amp; -1  &amp; \\  &amp;  &amp; 0\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{ccc}\frac{1}{2}  &amp;  0  &amp;  \frac{1}{2} \\ \frac{1}{2}  &amp;  0  &amp;  -\frac{1}{2} \\ 0  &amp;  1  &amp;  0\end{array}\right)\\=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0 \\ 1  &amp;  1  &amp;  0\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{ccc}\frac{1}{2}  &amp;  0  &amp;  \frac{1}{2} \\ \frac{1}{2}  &amp;  0  &amp;  -\frac{1}{2} \\ 0  &amp;  1  &amp;  0\end{array}\right)\\=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0 \\ 1  &amp;  0  &amp;  0\end{array}\right) \end{array} </me>  </p> 

                        <p> 即  <m> \boldsymbol{A}=\left(\begin{array}{lll}0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0 \\ 1  &amp;  0  &amp;  0\end{array}\right) </m> . </p> 

                        <p> (II)法2: 对  <m> 1,-1,0 </m>  的所有特征向量进行单位化, </p> 

                        <p>  <me> \boldsymbol{\eta}_{1}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}(1,0,1)^{\mathrm{T}}, \boldsymbol{\eta}_{2}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}(1,0,-1)^{\mathrm{T}},  \boldsymbol{\eta}_{3}=(0,1,0)^{\mathrm{T}}, </me>  </p> 

                        <p> 则   <m> \boldsymbol{Q}=\left(\boldsymbol{\eta}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\eta}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\eta}_{3}\right) </m>  为正交矩阵, 且  <m> \boldsymbol{Q}^{\mathrm{T}} \boldsymbol{A} \boldsymbol{Q}=\boldsymbol{Q}^{-1} \boldsymbol{A} \boldsymbol{Q}=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}1  &amp;  \\ &amp;  -1  &amp;  \\ &amp;   &amp;  0\end{array}\right), </m>  </p> 

                        <p> 所以 
                        <me> 
                        \begin{array}{l}
                        \boldsymbol{A}=\boldsymbol{Q}\left(\begin{array}{lll}1  &amp;   &amp;  \\  &amp;  -1  &amp;  \\  &amp;   &amp;  0\end{array}\right) \boldsymbol{Q}^{-1}=\boldsymbol{Q}\left(\begin{array}{lll}1  &amp;   &amp;  \\  &amp;  -1  &amp;  \\  &amp;   &amp;  0\end{array}\right) \boldsymbol{Q}^{\mathrm{T}}\\
                        =\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
                        \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}  &amp;  \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}  &amp;  0 \\
                        0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1 \\
                        \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}  &amp;  -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}  &amp;  0
                        \end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{lll}
                        1  &amp;   &amp;  \\
                        &amp;  -1  &amp;  \\
                        &amp;   &amp;  0
                        \end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
                        \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}  &amp;  0  &amp;  \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} \\
                        \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}  &amp;  0  &amp;  -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} \\
                        0  &amp;  1  &amp;  0
                        \end{array}\right)\\=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
                        \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}  &amp;  -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}  &amp;  0 \\
                        0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0 \\
                        \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}  &amp;  \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}  &amp;  0
                        \end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
                        \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}  &amp;  0  &amp;  \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} \\
                        \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}  &amp;  0  &amp;  -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} \\
                        0  &amp;  1  &amp;  0
                        \end{array}\right) \\
                        =\left(\begin{array}{lll}
                        0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1 \\
                        0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0 \\
                        1  &amp;  0  &amp;  0
                        \end{array}\right)
                        \end{array}
                        </me>  </p> 

                        <p> 即   <m> \boldsymbol{A}=\left(\begin{array}{lll}0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1 \\0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0 \\1  &amp;  0  &amp;  0\end{array}\right) </m>
                            
                    </p>
                </answer>
            </exercise>


