    <subsection>
        <title>二次型</title>    

        <exercises xml:id="exercises-la5_3">
            <title>练习题</title>   
            <!-- Q14 -->
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        二次型  <m> f\left(x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}\right)=x_{1}^{2}+a x_{2}^{2}+x_{3}^{2}+2 x_{1} x_{2}+2 a x_{1} x_{3}+2 x_{2} x_{3} </m>  的秩为  <m> 2 </m>  ,则  <m> a= </m>  ____ 
                    </p>
                </statement>
                <answer>
                    <p>
                        解: 二次型  <m> f </m>  的秩为  <m> 2 </m>  , 即矩阵  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  的秩为  <m> 2 </m>  .
                        由于<m> \boldsymbol{A}=\left(\begin{array}{lll}
                        1  &amp;  1  &amp;  a \\
                        1  &amp;  a  &amp;  1 \\
                        a  &amp;  1  &amp;  1
                        \end{array}\right) </m> . 由  <m> |\boldsymbol{A}|=-(a-1)^{2}(a+2)=0 </m> , 知  <m> a=1 </m>  或  <m> a=-2 </m> . 易知  <m> a=1 </m>  时,  <m> r(A)=1 </m> ,  <m> a=-2 </m>  时,  <m> r(A)=2 </m> , 故  <m> a=-2 </m> 

                    </p>
                </answer>
            </exercise>

            <!-- Q15 -->
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        二次型  <m> f\left(x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}\right)=x_{1}^{2}+3 x_{2}^{2}+x_{3}^{2}+2 x_{1} x_{2}+2 x_{1} x_{3}+2 x_{2} x_{3} </m> ,则  <m> f </m>  的正惯性指数为_____ 

                    </p>
                </statement>
                <answer>
                    <p>
                        解：法1:正交变换法  
                        <m> f </m>  对应的矩阵是  <m> \boldsymbol{A}=\left(\begin{array}{lll}1  &amp;  1  &amp;  1 \\ 1  &amp;  3  &amp;  1 \\ 1  &amp;  1  &amp;  1\end{array}\right) </m> 
                        
                        <me>  |\lambda \boldsymbol{E}-\boldsymbol{A}|=\left|\begin{array}{ccc}\lambda-1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  -1 \\ -1  &amp;  \lambda-3  &amp;  -1 \\ -1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  \lambda-1\end{array}\right| \stackrel{r_{1}-r_{3}}{=}\left|\begin{array}{ccc}\lambda  &amp;  0  &amp;  -\lambda \\ -1  &amp;  \lambda-3  &amp;  -1 \\ -1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  \lambda-1\end{array}\right| \stackrel{c_{3}+c_{1}}{=}\left|\begin{array}{ccc}\lambda  &amp;  0  &amp;  0 \\ -1  &amp;  \lambda-3  &amp;  -2 \\ -1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  \lambda-2\end{array}\right| \\=\lambda[(\lambda-3)(\lambda-2)-2]=\lambda\left(\lambda^{2}-5 \lambda+4\right)=\lambda(\lambda-4)(\lambda-1)
                        </me>  </p> 

                        <p>  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  的特征值为  <m> 0,1,4 </m> ,  <m> f </m>  的正惯性指数为  <m> 2 </m> . </p> 

                        <p> 法2:
                        <me> 
                        \begin{array}{l}
                        f\left(x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}\right)=x_{1}^{2}+3 x_{2}^{2}+x_{3}^{2}+2 x_{1} x_{2}+2 x_{1} x_{3}+2 x_{2} x_{3} \\
                        =\left(x_{1}+x_{2}+x_{3}\right)^{2}+2 x_{2}^{2}=y_{1}^{2}+y_{2}^{2} 
                        \end{array}
                        </me>  </p> 

                        <p>  <m> f </m>  的正惯性指数为 <m> 2 </m> 
                    </p>
                </answer>
            </exercise>

            <!-- Q16 -->
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        设二次型  <m> f\left(x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}\right)=x_{1}^{2}-x_{2}^{2}+2 a x_{1} x_{3}+4 x_{2} x_{3} </m>  负惯性指数为  <m> 1 </m>  ,则  <m> a </m>  的取值范围是_______

                    </p>
                </statement>
                <answer>
                    <p>
                        解: 由配方法知: 
                    <me> 
                    \begin{array}{l}
                    f\left(x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}\right)=x_{1}^{2}-x_{2}^{2}+2 a x_{1} x_{3}+4 x_{2} x_{3} \\
                    =x_{1}^{2}+2 a x_{1} x_{3}+a^{2} x_{3}^{2}-x_{2}^{2}+4 x_{2} x_{3}-a^{2} x_{3}^{2} \\
                    =\left(x_{1}+a x_{3}\right)^{2}-\left(x_{2}^{2}-4 x_{2} x_{3}+4 x_{3}^{2}\right)-a^{2} x_{3}^{2}+4 x_{3}^{2} \\
                    =\left(x_{1}+a x_{3}\right)^{2}-\left(x_{2}-2 x_{3}\right)^{2}+\left(4-a^{2}\right) x_{3}^{2}
                    \end{array}
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 由于  <m> f\left(x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}\right) </m>  的负惯性指数为  <m> 1,4-a^{2} \geq 0 </m>  从而  <m> -2 \leq a \leq 2 </m> . 
                    </p>
                </answer>
            </exercise>

            <!-- Q17 -->
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        已知实二次型  <m> f=a\left(x_{1}^{2}+x_{2}^{2}+x_{3}^{2}\right)+4 x_{1} x_{2}+4 x_{1} x_{3}+4 x_{2} x_{3} </m> 经正交变换可成标准形  <m> f=6 y_{1}^{2} </m> , 则  <m> a= </m>  ______

                    </p>
                </statement>
                <answer>
                    <p>
                        解:  <m> f </m>  的矩阵是  <m> \boldsymbol{A}=\left(\begin{array}{lll}a  &amp;  2  &amp;  2 \\ 2  &amp;  a  &amp;  2 \\ 2  &amp;  2  &amp;  a\end{array}\right) </m> , 因为  <m> f </m>  标准形为  <m> 6 y_{1}^{2} </m> ,所以  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  特征值为  <m> 6,0,0 </m> . 所以  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  可相似对角化:  <m> \boldsymbol{A} \sim \boldsymbol{\Lambda}=\left(\begin{array}{lll}6  &amp;   &amp;  \\  &amp;  0  &amp;  \\  &amp;   &amp;  0\end{array}\right) \Rightarrow \operatorname{tr}(\boldsymbol{A})=\operatorname{tr}(\boldsymbol{\Lambda}) </m>  </p> 

                    <p> 所以  <m> 3 a=6 </m> , 得  <m> a=2 </m> . 
                    </p>
                </answer>
            </exercise>

            <!-- Q18 -->
                <exercise>
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            设  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  是  <m> 3 </m>  阶实对称矩阵,  <m> \boldsymbol{E} </m>  是  <m> 3 </m>  阶单位矩阵. 若  <m> \boldsymbol{A}^{2}+\boldsymbol{A}=2 \boldsymbol{E} </m> ,且  <m> |\boldsymbol{A}|=4 </m> , 则二次型  <m> \boldsymbol{x}^{\mathrm{T}} \boldsymbol{A} \boldsymbol{x} </m>  的规范形为 ( ).

                        </p>
                    </statement>
                    <choices>
                        <choice>
                            <statement>
                                <p>
                                    <m> y_{1}^{2}+y_{2}^{2}+y_{3}^{2} </m> 
                                </p>
                            </statement>
                        </choice>
                        
                        <choice>
                            <statement>
                                <p>
                                    <m> y_{1}^{2}+y_{2}^{2}-y_{3}^{2} </m>
